    • Field Detail

      • ActionBar

        public static final int[] ActionBar
        ============================================ Attributes used to style the Action Bar. These should be set on your theme; the default actionBarStyle will propagate them to the correct elements as needed. Please Note: when overriding attributes for an ActionBar style you must specify each attribute twice: once with the "android:" namespace prefix and once without.

        Includes the following attributes:

        Attribute Description
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:background Specifies a background drawable for the action bar.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:backgroundSplit Specifies a background drawable for the bottom component of a split action bar.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:backgroundStacked Specifies a background drawable for a second stacked row of the action bar.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:customNavigationLayout Specifies a layout for custom navigation.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:displayOptions Options affecting how the action bar is displayed.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:divider Specifies the drawable used for item dividers.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:height Specifies a fixed height.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:homeLayout Specifies a layout to use for the "home" section of the action bar.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:icon Specifies the drawable used for the application icon.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:indeterminateProgressStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an indeterminate progress spinner.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:itemPadding Specifies padding that should be applied to the left and right sides of system-provided items in the bar.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:logo Specifies the drawable used for the application logo.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:navigationMode The type of navigation to use.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:progressBarPadding Specifies the horizontal padding on either end for an embedded progress bar.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:progressBarStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an embedded progress bar.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:subtitle Specifies subtitle text used for navigationMode="normal"
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:subtitleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for subtitle text.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:title Specifies title text used for navigationMode="normal"
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:titleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for title text.
        See Also:
        ActionBar_background, ActionBar_backgroundSplit, ActionBar_backgroundStacked, ActionBar_customNavigationLayout, ActionBar_displayOptions, ActionBar_divider, ActionBar_height, ActionBar_homeLayout, ActionBar_icon, ActionBar_indeterminateProgressStyle, ActionBar_itemPadding, ActionBar_logo, ActionBar_navigationMode, ActionBar_progressBarPadding, ActionBar_progressBarStyle, ActionBar_subtitle, ActionBar_subtitleTextStyle, ActionBar_title, ActionBar_titleTextStyle

      • ActionBarWindow

        public static final int[] ActionBarWindow
        These attributes are meant to be specified and customized by the app. The system will read and apply them as needed. These attributes control properties of the activity window, such as whether an action bar should be present and whether it should overlay content.

        Includes the following attributes:

        Attribute Description
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:windowActionBar
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:windowActionBarOverlay
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:windowFixedHeightMajor A fixed height for the window along the major axis of the screen, that is, when in portrait.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:windowFixedHeightMinor A fixed height for the window along the minor axis of the screen, that is, when in landscape.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:windowFixedWidthMajor A fixed width for the window along the major axis of the screen, that is, when in landscape.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:windowFixedWidthMinor A fixed width for the window along the minor axis of the screen, that is, when in portrait.
        es.ugr.deportesugrapp:windowSplitActionBar
        See Also:
        ActionBarWindow_windowActionBar, ActionBarWindow_windowActionBarOverlay, ActionBarWindow_windowFixedHeightMajor, ActionBarWindow_windowFixedHeightMinor, ActionBarWindow_windowFixedWidthMajor, ActionBarWindow_windowFixedWidthMinor, ActionBarWindow_windowSplitActionBar

        public static final int ActionBarWindow_windowActionBar
